quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  48,1,"Inna fatahna laka fathanmubeena"
  48,2,"Liyaghfira laka Allahu mataqaddama min thanbika wama taakhkhara wayutimmaniAAmatahu AAalayka wayahdiyaka siratan mustaqeema"
  48,3,"Wayansuraka Allahu nasranAAazeeza"
  48,4,"Huwa allathee anzala assakeenatafee quloobi almu/mineena liyazdadoo eemanan maAAaeemanihim walillahi junoodu assamawatiwal-ardi wakana Allahu AAaleeman hakeema"
  48,5,"Liyudkhila almu/mineena walmu/minatijannatin tajree min tahtiha al-anharukhalideena feeha wayukaffira AAanhum sayyi-atihimwakana thalika AAinda Allahi fawzan AAatheema"
  48,6,"WayuAAaththiba almunafiqeena walmunafiqatiwalmushrikeena walmushrikati aththanneenabillahi thanna assaw-iAAalayhim da-iratu assaw-i waghadiba AllahuAAalayhim walaAAanahum waaAAadda lahum jahannama wasaat maseera"
  48,7,"Walillahi junoodu assamawatiwal-ardi wakana Allahu AAazeezan hakeema"
  48,8,"Inna arsalnaka shahidanwamubashshiran wanatheera"
  48,9,"Litu/minoo billahi warasoolihiwatuAAazziroohu watuwaqqiroohu watusabbihoohu bukratan waaseela"
